playstore_details.title: HPE IceWall Smart OTP
playstore_details.description:
Important :
This application is designed to work with HPE IceWall Smart OTP*.
In order to use this application, it is necessary to install HPE IceWall on the server.
If those middlewares are not installed on the server, you cannot use this application.

HPE IceWall Smart OTP is an application for smartphones that allows you to perform multi-factor authentication by entering the OTP(One Time Password). Only once at the beginning, you need to do registration of User Account and key of OTP on the smartphone. When you enter the User password in the login page, you can login to the Web sites using the OTP. OTP of HPE IceWall Smart OTP is compliant with OATH.

* HPE IceWall, Web single sign-on solution originally developed by HPE Japan and marketed for the global markets, provides a highly convenient and comfortable yet highly secure environment. Since its first release in 1997, HPE IceWall has seen its adoption in intranet, B-to-C, B-to-B, and many other services globally with more than 40 million user licenses sold so far all over the world.

* HPE IceWall Smart OTP android is built using open source software.
For more information on opensource licensing, see the following URL:
https://h50146.www5.hpe.com/products/software/security/icewall/sso/iwso_android_oss.html
